prompt.prompt: Create a landscape full body image of a future-alien, paladin-themed military figure. Capture the essence of surrealism and heavy symbolism for hints of Rafal Olbinski's style, calculating the intricate use of light and shadow to define his work. Consider the vibrant colours, the otherworldly settings, and the intricate details that are the hallmark of late 19th century surrealism, avoiding post-1912 influences. Use an appropriate medium such as oil on canvas to emulate this.
